Looking for a way to continue to live by the PJ’s motto of “These Things We Do, That Other’s May Live,” Dom decided to deepen his practice and get certified as a Yoga Alliance, 200 hr RYT through Reyn Studios in New Orleans, LA. Dom has a passion for helping people and offering opportunities for someone to learn to become the best version of themselves. Join Dominic in one of his classes as he will guide you through your journey of connecting deeply with yourself.`,
    socialLink: null,
  },
  {
    name: "Teresa Cantrelle",
