    bio: `**Jacqueline “Jax” Hurst** has been teaching yoga since 2017, creating spaces rooted in authenticity, inner work, and light. In 2023, she began working alongside Love More and its founders to support their soft rebrand — helping bring their vision and mission to life in a way that feels embodied, intentional, and aligned.

Through her business, **The Invitation**, Jax partners with Love More to offer virtual yoga and meditation classes so students can stay connected to their practice wherever they are in the world. She also leads yoga sculpt teacher trainings at the studio and co-hosts the Women’s Wellness Retreat in Sedona with JoEllen.

