    bio: `Everyone is on a yoga journey, a path to union of body, mind, and soul. It’s called life. Some choose the mat as a place of movement and deep reflection for part of this journey. Katelyn first found her way to the mat in 2009 after a big transition and has since then been using her mat to move through whatever it is that needs transforming. On her mat, Katelyn has found presence, and empowerment, and has learned how to regulate her emotional state through movements linked with breath. 

