    title: "200HR RYT",
    image: getTeamImage("../assets/images/team/amber-ostoff.jpg"),
    bio: `Amber believes yoga is for every body and every season of life. Yoga offers a space to return to yourself, cultivate resilience, and create balance amidst life’s challenges. Amber’s classes are designed to leave you feeling grounded, empowered, and glowing—from the inside out.

Yoga has been a meaningful part of Amber’s life for many years. She was first introduced to the practice 18 years ago, while earning her Bachelor’s of Science in Exercise Science, Business Administration and Communication Studies. She quickly fell in love with the way yoga united breath and movement, while building both physical strength and inner calm. What began as a tool for athletics soon became a lifelong practice of grounding, healing, and discovery.

