Amber brings a deep passion for helping others feel confident, balanced, and connected. By day, she is a master holistic advanced practice aesthetician and owner of Glowing Skin by AmberWavezzz. In her business she specializes in advanced facials, nervous system regulation, energy work, non-toxic living, whole-body skincare, root-cause approach, and personalized treatments that support beauty from the inside out. She holds private and group containers for connection and healing, as well immersive sessions. 

