    image: getTeamImage("../assets/images/team/kat-parker.jpg"),
    bio: `Kat Parker is a Certified Yoga Instructor, NLP-Certified Leadership & Life Coach, and space-holder for transformation, on and off the mat.
Kat found yoga in 2023 after being invited to Love More yoga class. She had never practiced before, but what started as trying something new quickly became something she couldn’t live without.
