Outside of the studio, Kat uses yoga as an extension of her leadership coaching, helping women to build strength in their bodies, clarity in their minds, and confidence in how they show up in their lives. 


Follow Kat on IG at @thekatparker
`,
    socialLink: {"label":"Instagram","url":"https://www.instagram.com/thekatparker/"},
