    image: getTeamImage("../assets/images/team/allison-poswalk.jpg"),
    bio: `Allison is a 200-hour certified yoga teacher, trained through Love More University (November 2025) with over 30 years of personal practice, leading dynamic, strong and fun hot, warm and non-heated flows. Her classes are playful and real. You will move, build strength, laugh and try new things in a supportive, no-pressure space. Expect guided flow, options for all levels, and the freedom to push or pause as you need. You’ll leave feeling better than when you walked in.  `,
